label: emmisionNorm
comment: The standards set up by the Indian government which specify the amount of air pollutants from internal combustion engines, including those that vehicles can emit.

label: modelInfo
comment: The make/model information of the vehicle corresponding to this observation.

label: licensePlate
comment: The vehicle registration number corresponding to this observation.

label: issualDate
comment: The date of issual of license or a service such as insurance corresponding to this observation.

label: expiryDate
comment: The date of issual of license or a service such as insurance corresponding to this observation.

label: registrationDate
comment: The date on which a particular item or entity becomes officially recognized, authorized or approved according to the relevant regulations, procedures or requirements.

label: leasingEntity
comment: The information about the entity which leases the vehicle/machinery for agricultural purposes.

label: productType
comment: The type of agricultural product corresponding to this observation.

label: registeringAuthority
comment: The name of the entity authorised to collect and/or verify user details for the issual of a digital certificate.

label: personnelInfo
comment: Personnel information of an individual or business corresponding to this observation.

label: insuranceInfo
comment: The information about the insurance for the product or equipment corresponding to this observation.

label: subsidyAmount
comment: The amount of government subsidy for a product corresponding to this observation for the welfare of the people.

label: ownershipType
comment: The type of ownership of the entity corresponding to this observation. ENUM: [Lease, Rent, Own]

label: vehicleID
comment: The unique ID or code of the vehicle corresponding to this observation

label: purposeDescription
comment: Describes the purpose of the entity or service corresponding to this observation.

label: hsCode
comment: The Harmonized System (HS) code provided by the FAO (Food and Agricultural Organization) for the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: capitalInfo
comment: The income and expenditure information corresponding to the entity.

label: localeInfo
comment: Locale information corresponding to this observation.

label: deviceInfo
comment: The information of the device/sensor used in/for the entity/ service  corresponding to this observation.

label: leasePeriod
comment: The duration or tenure of the lease for a entity corresponding to this observation.

label: registrationNumber
comment: The registration number of the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: productName
comment: Name of the product corresponding to this observation.

label: certificateInfo
comment: Date of issual, expiry/validity, renewal of the document/certificate corresponding to this observation.

label: ownerInfo
comment: Details of the person who owns the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: lessorInfo
comment: Details of the person who leases the entity corresponding to this observation.
